commandlist:
!roll 

!ping 

!status 

!foo 

!help [Optional argument: Profile, Top, Convert] 

!twitch 

!youtube 

!steam 

!mcount [Optional argument: Mention a member] : Check message count, or points. 

!level [Optional argument: Mention a member] : Check level.

!status 

!stl : Set Twitch link. Usage: !stl (link) 

!syl : Set Youtube link. Usage: !syl (link) 

!ssl : Set Steam link. Usage : !ssl (link) 

!setlinks : Set all links in one message. Usage : !setlinks (Twitch) (Youtube) (Steam) 

!profile [Optional argument: Mention a Member] : View your profile! Detailed use: !help profile 

!server : Detailed server information. 

!top : Check top 10 in the server. Detailed use: !help top
